metadata.name: Oshizushi Tamago #59 #1/7
metadata.description: Indulge in the delightful Oshizushi Tamago, a sushi lover's paradise. It features fluffy white rice, crowned with a layer of savory tamago. The main piece is a slice of lotus root on top, followed by a dollop of Japanese mayonnaise. All of this is sprinkled with finely chopped chives for a visually appealing and flavorful garnish.
